cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "OPERATE-FR v0.1 — Freshness Routing Track (candidate operational benchmark)"
message: "If you use this artifact, please cite the specification document and the harness commit."
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Toeda
    given-names: Taiko
    affiliation: "MOBIUS LLC"
date-released: "2026-05-16"
version: "0.1.0"
abstract: >
  OPERATE-FR is a route-first freshness evaluation track. The v0.1
  artifact ships a 100-task Smoke-100 subset with per-task route labels,
  a transparent rule-based route classifier, a scorer that reports a
  component vector (no composite), and a harness for OpenAI-compatible
  and local model adapters. OPERATE-FR is a candidate operational
  benchmark track, not a standard benchmark.
keywords:
  - benchmark
  - freshness
  - routing
  - operational evaluation
  - non-assertion
